Nick was named Vice President, General Counsel and Secretary on October 1, 2015.  Prior to this, he served as the company’s Vice President, Associate General Counsel and Assistant Secretary. Nick joined Hillenbrand in 2011, after six years in private practice with Troutman Sanders in Atlanta, Georgia.






